    <item>
      <title>Pray Always</title>
      <link>http://www.lds.org/general-conference/2008/10/pray-always?lang=eng</link>
      <description>Prayer becomes more meaningful as we counsel with the Lord in all of our doings, as we express heartfelt gratitude, and as we pray for others.</description>
